### RescueGuide API - FirstHelp Controller Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5238/api/firsthelp

### Get all first help items
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get first help item by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Get first help item by ID (non-existent)
GET {{baseUrl}}/999

### Create new first help item
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 6,
  "name": "Beatmung",
  "description": "Künstliche Beatmung durchführen"
}

### Create another first help item
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 7,
  "name": "Herzdruckmassage",
  "description": "Herzdruckmassage durchführen bei Herzstillstand"
}

### Update first help item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Beatmung - Aktualisiert",
  "description": "Aktualisierte Anleitung zur künstlichen Beatmung"
}

### Delete first help item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1

### Delete non-existent first help item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/999

### Update non-existent first help item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 999,
  "name": "Test Help",
  "description": "Test Description"
}

